{"tid":1859004,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 警告你地千祈唔好\"袋住先\"","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T07:17:19.000Z","uid":137291,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c31a5ff10229e2a0d76acad393d3a8212c737b24","tid":1859004,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"港共政府好明顯係想滅絕香港人先會一直冇封關又唔派口罩<br />\n但係嚟緊兩個星期封關嘅機會都幾大<br />\n因為封關後更有效達到目的<br />\n原因有三:<br />\n1. 大陸人已經落咗好多過嚟, 已經足夠去散播病毒毒害香港人<br />\n2. 回應三罷(特別係醫護罷工), 做show俾港豬/藍絲睇佢地回應咗訴求<br />\n3. 封關將會封曬出入境, 由得你地班香港人同病毒困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n所以我同你地講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好袋住先</span></span></strong><br />\n封關後我地要有新嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">港人訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 立即分發政府口罩存貨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 立即譴返近兩個月到訪香港的湖北省人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 承諾不在民居附近設隔離營</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 制裁賣二手/假口罩之商戶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟技窮   冇乜政治頭腦<br />\n希望大家幫手補充/改善<br />\n總之我想帶出嘅消息係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好接受政府遲來的回應</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"01b564af6bc6aa68abf26c24d056d96d37013141","tid":1859004,"uid":192480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好袋住先<br />\n千祈唔好袋住先<br />\n千祈唔好袋住先<br />\n<br />\n好重要!"},{"pid":"2562b47e375a48b25dd2a374ad7d0b93fc5d6ac6","tid":1859004,"uid":38766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"除左封關外<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"da4c601e795a52706a5cd7a02afc9c735da620e4","tid":1859004,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士</span></span>：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=da3e095f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡抗沙士</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857672</a></span></span> <br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=18411252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"0de4665d9bb89ff728072a9a7b181a22ba01e6fa","tid":1859004,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2562b47e375a48b25dd2a374ad7d0b93fc5d6ac6","tid":1859004,"uid":38766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"除左封關外<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"唔想叫五大訴求<br />\n1. 因為想拉攏藍絲, 而藍絲潛意識好抗拒五大訴求呢個term<br />\n2. 唔想撈亂新舊"},{"pid":"cc2038a87253f8e5d1638853816dc8760985b664","tid":1859004,"uid":137291,"li